<http://model.geneontology.org/ev_w_id_R-HSA-452100_RO_0002234_R-ALL-29370_cytosol_Reactome_R-HSA-452100_R-HSA-452100_enabled_by_UniProt_P23458_R-HSA-452100_controller>
